{"lemma":"خُطْبَة","slug":"خُطْبَة","root":"خ.ط.ب","root_slug":"خ-ط-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ط-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"خُطْبَة","root":"خطب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10972","n10978","n10979"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8F%D8%B7%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of خَطَبَ (ḵaṭaba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"betrothal, engagement (commitment prior to marriage)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"speech, oration, harangue"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"speech, oration, harangue; khutbah, Friday sermon"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"impure color, dirt color"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root خ ط ب (ḵ ṭ b), related to addressing people with a message, hence the senses “ask in marriage” and “preach”."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10972","headword_ar":"خطّبهُ","root":"xTb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He granted his request of a woman in marriage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AxTbhu","text_ar":"اخطبهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n10978","headword_ar":"خُطْبَةٌ","root":"xTb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", a word of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEolapN","text_ar":"فُعْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlapN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nusoxapN","text_ar":"نُسْخَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manosuwxapN","text_ar":"مَنْسُوخَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gurofapN mina AlmaA='i","text_ar":"غُرْفَةٌ مِنَ المَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magoruwfapN","text_ar":"مَغْرُوفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An exhortation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"admonition"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recited by a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaTiyb","text_ar":"خَطِيب"},{"kind":"text","text":"] : (Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a form of words, a discourse, a sermon, a speech, an oration,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a harangue, which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaTiyb","text_ar":"خَطِيب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recites on the pulpit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA:) [in the noon-service of the congregational mosque on Friday, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xTyb","text_ar":"خطيب"},{"kind":"text","text":"recites two forms of words, each of which is thus termed: the former chiefly consists of expressions of praise to God, blessings on Mohammad and his family and companions, and exhortation to the congregation; and is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTobapu AlwaEoZi","text_ar":"خُطْبَةُ الوَعْظِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": the latter, of praise to God, exhortation, blessings on Mo- hammad and his family and companions, and prayer for the Muslims in general, and especially for the Sovereign; and is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTobapu Aln~aEoti","text_ar":"خُطْبَةُ النَّعْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (see my “ Modern Egyptians, ” ch. iii.:)] or, [accord. to its original signification,] with the [Pagan] Arabs,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a discourse, a speech, an oration,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a harangue,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[generally applied to one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delivered in public,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in rhyming prose;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-Is-hák, K:) or the old Arabian"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTobap","text_ar":"خُطْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Pagan and the early Muslim ages, was,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in most instances, not in rhyming prose;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the term “ prose, ” as here used, does not exclude what contains poetry introduced by way of testimony and the like: (MF:) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a tract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small treatise"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discourse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"risaAlap","text_ar":"رِسَالَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is complete in itself, or,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in other words,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has a beginning and an end:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTabN","text_ar":"خُطَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxaATibu","text_ar":"مَخَاطِبُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in the following words of a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino A^aholi AlmaHaA$idi waAlmaxaATibi","text_ar":"مِنْ اَهْلِ المَحَاشِدِ وَالمَخَاطِبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of those who congregate, and harangue people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"exciting them to go forth and assemble for seditious purposes, is said to be used in the same sense as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTab","text_ar":"خُطَب"},{"kind":"text","text":", and to be a pl. [of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTobapN","text_ar":"خُطْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], contr. to rule, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aAbihu","text_ar":"مَشَابِهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abahN","text_ar":"شَبَهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malaAmiHu","text_ar":"مَلَامِحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lamoHapN","text_ar":"لَمْحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or it is pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoTabapN","text_ar":"مَخْطَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTobapN","text_ar":"خُطْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or it [is pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoTabN","text_ar":"مَخْطَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and] signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"places of haranguing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H$d","text_ar":"حشد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTobapF HasanapF","text_ar":"خُطْبَةً حَسَنَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaTaba AlxaTiybu","text_ar":"خَطَبَ الخَطِيبُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xTyb","text_ar":"خطيب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recited a beautiful"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xTbp","text_ar":"خطبة"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiTobN","text_ar":"خِطْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"-A3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A turbid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dusky, colour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a colour inclining to turbidness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"duskiness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mixed with yellowish red;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the colour of wheat before it dries, and that of some wild asses:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a green"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. here meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a dark,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an ashy, dust-"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"colour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a dust-colour suffused with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuDorap","text_ar":"خُضْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a dark,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an ashy, dust-colour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoTabu","text_ar":"اَخْطَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] (A, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuDorap","text_ar":"خُضْرَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mixed with black."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  The saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albay~inu AlxuTobapi","text_ar":"البَيِّنُ الخُطْبَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anota AlA^axoTabu","text_ar":"اَنْتَ الاَخْطَبُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which might be imagined to ascribe to the person addressed perspicuity, or eloquence, in his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTobap","text_ar":"خُطْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", really means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou art"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the asinine;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he who bears evidence of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHimaAriy~ap","text_ar":"الحِمَارِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asinineness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","MF","T","TA","K","A"]},{"entry_id":"n10979","headword_ar":"خِطْبَةٌ","root":"xTb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaTaba AlmaroA^apa","text_ar":"خَطَبَ المَرْاَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, A, K:) or a simple subst. (Msb.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiTobN","text_ar":"خِطْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":["S","A","K"]}]}}